{{Infobox book| <!-- See Wikipedia:WikiProject_Novels or Wikipedia:WikiProject_Books --> | name = Creatures of the Night | image = | author = [[Sal Piro]] | cover_artist = | country = | language = English | series = | publisher = [[Caliber Comics|Stabur Press]] | subject = ''[[The Rocky Horror Picture Show]]'' | release_date = 1990 | media_type = | pages = 167 | isbn = 0-941613-12-7 | preceded_by = | followed_by = Creatures of the Night II }}
'''''Creatures of the Night: The Rocky Horror Experience''''' is a book about the cult following of the motion picture ''[[The Rocky Horror Picture Show]]'', written by [[Sal Piro]].<ref>[http://www.goodreads.com/book/show/1178334.Creatures_of_the_Night Goodreads]</ref><ref>[http://www.rocky-horror-france.com/sal-piro.html Rocky-horror-france.com]</ref><ref>{{cite web|page=263|publisher=[[Princeton University Press]]|date=2006|title=The American Musical and the Performance of Personal Identity|author=Knapp, Raymond|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Bx13uwK0pdIC&pg=PA263&lpg=PA263&dq=sal+piro+creatures+of+the+night+rocky+horror&source=bl&ots=UGGq6eaKE0&sig=9V5SyBqI029RwtA9NMjjt5R1wN4&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwinkpfCg_XPAhWmrFQKHUASBXw4ChDoAQgxMAU#v=onepage&q=sal%20piro%20creatures%20of%20the%20night%20rocky%20horror&f=false}}</ref>
Piro has been President of the National Fan club since 1977. The book contains information about the beginnings of the cult following as well as Piro's own experiences as a fan of the film.
